title: PROJECT Phase 1 - First Strike Chaches
body:
*sigh* 

I am still yet to receive my Project Champion Caches. 
I bought the 8220Rp Bundle on the FIRST DAY of the event. I've posted about this problem 3 times!
Everyone else I know has their blueprints and loading screen cards. So where are mine?
WHERE ARE MINE RIOT?!?!!! 

I just want what I paid for...
Get your stuff together,
Rosey93

replies.body:
Hey there,

Have you [submitted a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) to Player Support yet? They're the only ones who can assist with account specific inquiries.
